Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:53.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}未完成のパズル
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:17:01.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}どうしてだろう? 何かが足りない
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:07.04,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}行き違いの運命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:16.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}離れてゆくことも　知りながら
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:21.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}また歩く
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:28.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I Stay Alive
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:35.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}今は一人　闇をさまようだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:53.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}想定外の切なさが　胸の中　消えぬままで
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.36,0:16:53.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}尚未完成的拼图
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:17:01.70,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}这是为何  到底还欠缺什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:07.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}擦肩而过的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:16.05,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}虽然知道你终将离我而去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.97,0:17:21.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我仍会继续走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.14,0:17:28.48,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}我还能坚持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:35.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}即使现在只身一人徘徊在黑夜之中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.20,0:17:53.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}那意想不到的悲伤至今仍刺痛我的心房  定会铭肌镂骨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.90,0:24:30.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Oh, please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.24,0:24:32.32,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.74,0:24:37.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}No, don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.95,0:24:39.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.79,0:24:49.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}狂った時計　刻む命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.71,0:24:53.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}こぼれてく記憶の砂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.59,0:24:57.30,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}芽生えた想いまで
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.51,0:25:02.43,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}ねえ　こんなに呆気なく
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.39,0:25:09.65,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}消えてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.65,0:25:10.94,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}I wish I was there
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.94,0:25:12.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Oh, please don't let me die
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.15,0:25:15.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}Waiting for your touch
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.32,0:25:19.37,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}二度となにも失くさぬように
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:26.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}私を忘れて　始めて「Restart」
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.58,0:25:28.54,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}No, don't give up on life
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.75,0:25:30.63,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}This endless dead end
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.88,0:25:35.22,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}君を砕くこの悲しみが
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.59,0:25:40.51,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}いつか終わりますように
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.72,0:25:44.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.02,0:25:48.35,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}My time is spinning around
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.61,0:25:52.44,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}Your deep black eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.90,0:26:00.91,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)\fs30}I forgot what time it is And our memories are gone…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.37,0:26:05.04,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}甘い香り放つ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.21,0:26:09.00,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}追憶という名の罠
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.00,0:26:12.80,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}誘われ囚われ
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.05,0:26:17.80,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}なぜ抗えもせず　また
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.84,0:26:25.02,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}溺れてしまうの
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.14,0:26:26.39,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}I wish you were here
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.48,0:26:28.44,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}Oh, never close your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.44,0:26:30.40,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}Searching for a true fate
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.86,0:26:34.90,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}どこか消えたあのぬくもりを
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.24,0:26:41.74,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}追いかけ続けて　見失う「Restart」
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.99,0:26:44.08,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}So, let us try again
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.29,0:26:46.16,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}From the very first time
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.45,0:26:50.63,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}「きっときっと」そうやって今も
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.08,0:26:56.09,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}誰も皆演じている
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.21,0:27:00.01,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}For now I'll see you off
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.80,0:27:03.18,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}And we'll die
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.30,0:27:05.14,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.47,0:27:06.35,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}二度と…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.64,0:27:10.85,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}And we'll start
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.10,0:27:12.73,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}Waiting for a new day
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.23,0:27:14.40,EDJP1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(7,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}君と…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.90,0:24:30.11,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.24,0:24:32.32,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}你的触碰  我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.74,0:24:37.78,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}不  请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.95,0:24:39.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}尽管这绝望  不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.79,0:24:49.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}失准的时钟  记录着生命
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.71,0:24:53.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}散落满地的记忆之砂
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.59,0:24:57.30,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}以及萌生的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.51,0:25:02.43,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}你看  却是那么轻易
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.39,0:25:09.65,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}消失殆尽
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.65,0:25:10.94,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}我希望能与你同在
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.94,0:25:12.90,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}请不要让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.15,0:25:15.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}你的触碰  我的等待
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.32,0:25:19.37,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}为了不再失去曾经拥有的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.70,0:25:26.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}让我忘却自己的过去  重新开始旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.58,0:25:28.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}不  请不要对生命无爱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.75,0:25:30.63,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}尽管这绝望  不竭不衰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.88,0:25:35.22,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}愿那让你苦不堪言的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.59,0:25:40.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}会迎来完结的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.72,0:25:44.48,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(100,100)}我目送着你离去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.02,0:25:48.35,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}我的世界飞速旋转着
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.61,0:25:52.44,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}你那深邃的眼眸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.90,0:26:00.91,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}我忘却了时光 忘却了彼此的回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.37,0:26:05.04,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}香甜的气息芬芳四溢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.21,0:26:09.00,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}那名为追忆的圈套
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.00,0:26:12.80,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}引诱我步入其中并被其囚禁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.05,0:26:17.80,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}为何 连反抗之意都尚未萌生之时
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.84,0:26:25.02,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}就如此沉溺其中呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.14,0:26:26.39,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}我愿你在此
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.48,0:26:28.44,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}请睁开你的双眼
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.44,0:26:30.40,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}去寻找那份真切
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.86,0:26:34.90,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}那些许的温暖 究竟消失在何方
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.24,0:26:41.74,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}我不停追寻着 却再度遗失轮回的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.99,0:26:44.08,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}来 让我们再试一次
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.29,0:26:46.16,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}从我们最初相遇的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.45,0:26:50.63,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}此刻与你所描绘出的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.08,0:26:56.09,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}定是在故作坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.21,0:27:00.01,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}而我却要目送你离开
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.80,0:27:03.18,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.30,0:27:05.14,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.47,0:27:06.35,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}再一次的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.64,0:27:10.85,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}我们终将会重来
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.10,0:27:12.73,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}重来对新一天的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.23,0:27:14.40,EDCN1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1236,360)\blur3\fad(100,100)}与你携手迈进
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Comment,,0,0,0,,——Title——
